item.title: CVE-2023-3633|2024-08-02T07:01:57.364Z -- bitdefender -- engines
item.description: An out-of-bounds write vulnerability in Bitdefender Engines on Windows causes the engine to crash. This issue affects Bitdefender Engines version 7.94791 and lower.
